{"tid":1465270,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 屌你老母港共政府！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:22.000Z","uid":33543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec59928ab22b42c1d031f76ff56f86653d1abff","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"首先利申 核爆都唔割 唔係想分化 我唔係狗 我唔係鬼 我只不過係見到大家明明贏緊但係今日咁嘅情況真係好心痛<br />\n<br />\n首先我覺得十分認同勇武同如果冇勇武我地行唔到今時今日，多謝前線勇武。<br />\n<br />\n但係想大家諗返今次嘅革命唔係單靠勇武就可以成功，港共政府就係睇中我地有一班前線勇武佢地先可以派鬼入黎。所以希望大家分清楚咩叫勇武咩叫心口得個勇字！！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地明知有鬼，但係入得機場嘅你仲怕咩有鬼？<strong>機場5000支cctv影住你，仲勁過鬼嘅鏡頭啊！</strong><strong>機場鬼係咩？ 就係想你地分化，衝出去，俾理由俾藉口人清場！</strong>由依家起停止分化，停止捉鬼！ 唔好屌我住，睇埋落去先！<br />\n<br />\n其實和理非點解到今時今日都仲敢走出機場，係因為大家都相信只要係機場和理非，警狗就冇理由血腥鎮壓。而癱瘓機場好簡單，好似尋日咁，乜都冇做就可以癱瘓而唔需要主動去搞鳩旅客，反而係機場嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非應該要定deadline逼政府正面出黎面對事實仲要同海外旅客，記者做好文宣，宣傳deadline!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好誤會，我唔係叫勇武收皮，而其實呢幾日勇武應該要休息下回下氣升級裝備備戰。點解？ 如果港共仲係無視我地條deadline，呢個時候就係勇武出場。<br />\n<br />\n當然，細節係點，點樣升級全部都要再商量。但係要各位手足停止分化先商量到啊，唔好中港共政府計啊！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油 齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6f7deccc0fa871fbfbb48c433f1dec1c5eee7b36","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"debe8254ae8f0698897b19a0854ebf9a5cd696a2","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"cc89d37858f40741b0deb45cfe03ae5e75aaa528","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f77dbd7c994c9f4ec7f45e16985a5c7ccdb1b58a","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ba2a663e2ddaa5cf3a6508b73b2ec13316e89ba6","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"cf3275ec0bbf339ae1e08d3773a405617c0c0d6c","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0f838c34a8b57667f683196227e9b4e67cf64bfd","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"24f08948eca8b757bd744c8860709cf5d11e2080","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1fb69bb86d43748eba0bc85e85f5a99015a237ee","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:49.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1782ad1b0ec097445d7638323d894ad01305cbb4","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2ca91d153605faa1ff64e5adef3a2c5ac2cf56af","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43d28ce58c9b26b116277fa2a540f557eb5cb5df","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"134cb940d6e62005a2d7bfb09d737002b87bf10d","tid":1465270,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}